14
00:01:15,034 --> 00:01:16,077
Please, stop.

15
00:01:16,161 --> 00:01:18,496
And, Julia, do you choose to accept?

16
00:01:18,580 --> 00:01:19,581
Don't.

17
00:01:19,914 --> 00:01:22,125
- I do.
- No.

18
