29
00:02:55,051 --> 00:02:56,928
<i>The CIA's Special Activities Division</i>

30
00:02:57,011 --> 00:03:00,139
<i>has relentlessly hunted Lane's
elite network of hostiles.</i>

31
00:03:00,223 --> 00:03:02,559
<i>But many remain unknown and at large.</i>

32
00:03:02,809 --> 00:03:04,769
<i>The remnants of this
extremist splinter cell</i>

