I don't like it.

75
00:05:10,436 --> 00:05:13,690
Something about this guy
just really gives me the creeps.

76
00:05:13,773 --> 00:05:15,775
Okay, just relax.

77
00:05:15,858 --> 00:05:17,193
I'm relaxed.

78
00:05:17,276 --> 00:05:18,361
