<i>would require
highly specialized knowledge</i>

164
00:11:35,780 --> 00:11:37,406
<i>that very few people possess.</i>

165
00:11:37,990 --> 00:11:42,661
<i>The question now is who would attack
all three of these holy sites? And why?</i>

166
00:11:43,079 --> 00:11:46,165
<i>The attacks occurred
at precisely the same moment,</i>

167
00:11:46,248 --> 00:11:47,416
<i>just over an hour ago,</i>

168
00:11:47,708 --> 00:11:49,335
<i>at 4:00 a.m. Eastern Time.</i>

169
00:11:49,418 --> 00:11:50,920
<i>Within minutes of the attack...</i>

170
00:11:51,003 --> 00:11:53,381
<i>...Congress ordered
an emergency recess</i>

171
